and the only question is
how much social disruption

00:51:06.780 --> 00:51:08.850
we go through before we get there.

00:51:08.850 --> 00:51:10.990
Now you've got, oh,
there's something I can do.

00:51:10.990 --> 00:51:13.750
I just make sure my elected officials

00:51:13.750 --> 00:51:16.810
promote development of
renewable energy and, besides,

00:51:16.810 --> 00:51:18.725
that means we'll be in the driver's seat

